            "title": "Google Gemini在AI模型市場持續擴大市佔率",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Q6h6QwxW6sSH1MqrHXbmsg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA6U04V_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 根據經紀行Piper Sandler引用SEMRush數據顯示,Google的Gemini在AI模型競賽中持續取得進展,儘管其總用戶數仍落後於ChatGPT。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據顯示,Gemini在2026年3月吸引了約3.68億獨立訪客,而ChatGPT則約為7.77億。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但Gemini的獨立訪客市佔率在3月攀升至超過27%,較2025年8月的13.8%大幅上升,而ChatGPT則是主要的市佔率流失方。Anthropic的Claude在3月也獲得市佔率增長,從2月的5.0%上升至9.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2b0df280-9b2b-3f2e-b890-42591999f95c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">預測市場目前大幅看好Anthropic將在2026年6月底前擁有最佳AI模型。根據報告中引用的Polymarket數據,Anthropic以65%的隱含機率領先,而Google僅為21%——較2月的71%大幅下滑。Anthropic在3月初超越了Google。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時,Google的傳統搜尋業務持續面臨阻力。美國搜尋流量市佔率持續年減,儘管下滑速度正在放緩。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數據顯示,3月Google在美國的出站搜尋市佔率年減幅度略微收窄至負1.8%,較2月的負3.1%有所改善。在全球範圍內,Google的搜尋市佔率在3月年比大致持平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">微軟Bing在最近幾個月也穩步改善,3月達到2.3%的年增率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Piper Sandler還強調Meta宣布推出Muse Spark,這是其Meta Superintelligence Labs的首款產品,被視為建立具競爭力前沿模型的重要一步。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">初步基準測試數據顯示,Muse Spark較Llama 4 Maverick有顯著改進,值得注意的是這僅在團隊組建九個月後就達成。Piper表示將密切關注Meta如何利用其超過35億日活躍用戶的基礎來推動Meta AI的採用率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
